Ranger Help for: falcon eyes
=============================

SYNTAX:      falcon <direction>
USAGE:       forest,plains,swamp,desert,jungle,hills,road,beach,
             mountain,arctic,barren,outside
SLOT COST:   4
BASE SP:     20
SKILL TYPE:  scouting

SUMMARY:
This skill allows a Ranger to send a falcon to scout in a given
direction. The falcon flies ahead and reports back what lies in the
adjacent room, including any creatures or notable features. This is
useful for scouting dangerous areas before entering them. The detail
of the falcon's report depends on the Ranger's skill level.
